# Exclude local state, secrets, and non-infra material from any Terraform package
# or module upload (e.g. a registry publish or remote run). Patterns are relative
# to this module dir (infra/). The repo-root agent/dev entries are belt-and-
# suspenders for tooling that packages from a wider root.
.git
.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
crash.*.log
# real var files may hold values; the committed *.example template is fine to keep
terraform.tfvars
*.auto.tfvars
# repo-root local/dev material that must never ride along in an infra package
.agent/
.claude/
.codex/
.gemini/
dev/
